  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统的课堂服务设计一个状态流转图。核心场景是：当系统就绪后，服务从INIT进入STOPPED待命状态；然后触发ContentCDN的内容射出流程，到达最大限位后再返回最小限位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "TO_MAX",
        "RETURN_TO_MIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：INIT是初始状态，由ClassroomService触发。然后STOPPED到TO_MAX的转移条件是\"射出条件成立\"，并且关联ContentCDN。那从STOPPED返回INIT的情况呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "TO_MAX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ContentCDN负责内容分发，触发射出。另外还有一个分支：当GradeSync成绩同步模块报告系统就绪时，可以让STOPPED状态的服务重新回到INIT重新初始化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOPPED",
        "INIT",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "is_system_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：INIT到STOPPED的条件是is_system_ready为True，STOPPED到TO_MAX标注射出条件和ContentCDN。然后TO_MAX到RETURN_TO_MIN，以及RETURN_TO_MIN回到STOPPED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "STOPPED",
        "TO_MAX",
        "RETURN_TO_MIN",
        "is_system_ready",
        "ejection_maxlim_on",
        "ejection_minlim_on"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "限位传感器的命名需要准确：射出到最大位置时触发ejection_maxlim_on，返回最小位置时触发ejection_minlim_on。这两个条件分别控制TO_MAX到RETURN_TO_MIN，以及RETURN_TO_MIN到STOPPED的转移。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TO_MAX",
        "RETURN_TO_MIN",
        "STOPPED",
        "ejection_maxlim_on",
        "ejection_minlim_on"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新。现在检查STOPPED的两个出边：一个是到TO_MAX走ContentCDN射出流程，另一个是到INIT走GradeSync重初始化。两者的触发条件都是is_system_ready为True，这样会有歧义吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOPPED",
        "TO_MAX",
        "INIT",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "is_system_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "需要修正：STOPPED到INIT的转移应该明确标注是GradeSync触发的，虽然条件也是is_system_ready，但要在括号里注明模块来源，避免和INIT进入STOPPED的那条混淆。射出那条线保持原样，因为射出条件本身已经隐含了ContentCDN的上下文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOPPED",
        "INIT",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "is_system_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，STOPPED到INIT的转移现在标注为\"is_system_ready==True (Education_GradeSync)\"，而INIT到STOPPED只写\"is_system_ready==True\"。这样六条转移关系都清晰了：INIT↔STOPPED双向，STOPPED→TO_MAX→RETURN_TO_MIN→STOPPED形成射出循环。",
